PACT Manpower

OUR SERVICES

Since 1990, PACT Manpower Supply has been a leading company in the UAE when it comes to providing manpower for various requirements in the region. We are a registered labor supply company with our headquarters in Dubai and specialize in Civil Manpower Supply, Finishing and Gypsum Carpenters, General Helpers, Mechanical, Electrical and Plumbing Manpower Supply. What sets us apart from other Manpower companies in the region is the level we go to make sure our Manpower who is our greatest strength is always happy, taken care of and treated with respect while providing services of the utmost quality to our clients.

All our employees are recruited from different parts of the world making sure they have the considerable knowledge and hands on experience for the job. At PACT we believe that happier employees get the job done quickly and more efficiently. Being a duly registered company we make sure we provide our employees with proper transport, accomodation, medical insurance, annual activities and other benefits.
